						<summary>

						<p>This is not dated. It refers to the <hi rend="bold">(Chōḻa)</hi> king <hi rend="bold">Punyakomarān</hi> ruling over <hi rend="bold">Chirppuḷi,</hi> and records the death of a hero named <hi rend="bold">Parasurāman</hi> in a battle. On palaeographic grounds the record may be relegated to the 8th century A.D.</p>						

